Package: ros-jazzy-agni-tf-tools
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libboost-all-dev, ros-jazzy-angles, ros-jazzy-geometry-msgs, ros-jazzy-interactive-markers, ros-jazzy-pluginlib, ros-jazzy-rclcpp, ros-jazzy-rviz-common, ros-jazzy-rviz-default-plugins, ros-jazzy-std-msgs, ros-jazzy-tf2, ros-jazzy-tf2-geometry-msgs, ros-jazzy-tf2-ros, ros-jazzy-visualization-msgs, ros-jazzy-ros-workspace
Description: This package provides a gui program as well as a rviz plugin to publish static transforms.
 Both support the transformation between various Euler angle representations. The rviz plugin also allows to configure the transform with an interactive marker.
